{
  "id": "69a831e2d1d1202030b4702f",
  "title": "中国語の音韻",
  "created": 1772630501,
  "updated": 1772643815,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a831e2d1d1202030b4702f",
      "text": "中国語の音韻",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772630501,
      "updated": 1772630501
    },
    {
      "id": "69a831e40000000000bff212",
      "text": "中国語の音韻の複雑さの話題では声調についてよく言われるが、子音も母音も量が多く弁別もしづらい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772630501,
      "updated": 1772630588
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8323d0000000000bff215",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772630589,
      "updated": 1772630589
    },
    {
      "id": "69a843440000000000bff319",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772634949,
      "updated": 1772634949
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8323d0000000000bff216",
      "text": "音節の構造は",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772630590,
      "updated": 1772634948
    },
    {
      "id": "69a843450000000000bff31a",
      "text": "\t声調＋子音＋母音＋*/n/nŋ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772634950,
      "updated": 1772635001
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8437e0000000000bff31b",
      "text": " \tまず組み合わせ要素が多い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772635007,
      "updated": 1772635020
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8438e0000000000bff31c",
      "text": " \tそれぞれの子音と母音も多い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772635023,
      "updated": 1772635032
    },
    {
      "id": "69a843990000000000bff31d",
      "text": " \tつまり音節の組み合わせは極めて多い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772635034,
      "updated": 1772635055
    },
    {
      "id": "69a843ff0000000000bff31e",
      "text": "\t現代中国語で使用される完全な音節表なるものが作られている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772635135,
      "updated": 1772635155
    },
    {
      "id": "69a844130000000000bff31f",
      "text": " \t> 關於現代標準漢語使用的音節的完整列表（包含兒化音），",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772635155,
      "updated": 1772635169
    },
    {
      "id": "69a844180000000000bff320",
      "text": " \t> 請見[汉语拼音音节列表 https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/汉语拼音音节列表]與[漢語兒化韻表 https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/汉语拼音#汉语儿化韵表]。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772635161,
      "updated": 1772635330
    },
    {
      "id": "69a844240000000000bff322",
      "text": "  > [https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/現代標準漢語音系 現代標準漢語音系(zh)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772635173,
      "updated": 1772635194
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8433d0000000000bff318",
